 the big talking point, just how great the support has been for us out here.\", \"from\": 6279, \"to\": 6374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the big talking point\", \"from\": 6299, \"to\": 6320}, {\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 6337, \"to\": 6348}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 6362, \"to\": 6364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut yeah, I mean, I think I was in a certain mindset going into Tokyo and I left with a different mindset, just like I have done a lot of times in my career because I am ignorant and na\\u00c3\\u00afve and do not give things much thought.\", \"from\": 6376, \"to\": 6605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6443, \"end\": 6448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998393336852427, \"rank\": 0.00016069213216317403, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a certain mindset\", \"from\": 6414, \"to\": 6431}, {\"ngram\": \"a different mindset\", \"from\": 6465, \"to\": 6484}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 6508, \"to\": 6513}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 6517, \"to\": 6522}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 6526, \"to\": 6535}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 6585, \"to\": 6591}, {\"ngram\": \"much thought\", \"from\": 6592, \"to\": 6604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But once you experience things, you start to see what the hype is about.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Day has learned that as well as anyone.\", \"from\": 6606, \"to\": 6722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 6630, \"to\": 6636}, {\"ngram\": \"the hype\", \"from\": 6660, \"to\": 6668}, {\"ngram\": \"about.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Day\", \"from\": 6672, \"to\": 6685}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 6714, \"to\": 6720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s admitted 